{"about_the_game":"Containment Corps is an online multiplayer cooperative first person experience. The game combines elements of resource management and traditional FPS themes to create an exhilarating team-based encounter. <br><br>You and a team of specialized units have been called upon to quell an uprising of contaminated swamp creatures. Choose your loadout and coordinate your defense; utilize unique abilities and powerful turrets to repel the onslaught. Keep the operation running. Manage your crystal energy supply to maintain full-base functionality, upgrade defenses, and power up weapons. Collect more by harvesting dead enemies. <br><br>[Scaled Survival: Assemble a team to survive as long as possible. Play alone or with friends!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693830/extras/turret.gif?t=1634427247\" /><br><br>Equip various items to give unique abilities or perks some of which include:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Airstrike<br></li><li> Landmine<br></li><li> Stun trap<br></li><li> Grenades<br></li><li> Shotgun<br></li><li> Automatic Turret<br></li><li> Powershield</li></ul>And many more!<br><br>Play in one of three maps<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Swamp<br></li><li> Desert<br></li><li> Canyon</li></ul><br>It will take a well organized and balanced team to resist the hordes<br><br><i>How long can you survive?</i>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Just Getting Started!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/693830/b50d66fa9097107d15dcba59d0b4dc547e654ff9.jpg"},{"name":"Welcome to the Corps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/693830/8a4c6051a8c9850d634c249ae3f78df26fe9b1b7.jpg"},{"name":"Hard Corps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/693830/c0f63d4d05fac2406bd616b2126ca4cb59dc2144.jpg"},{"name":"Master Corps","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcomm